            <h4>A good website for an even greater dog.</h4>
            <p>This website was created over the span of roughly two months (July - August 2020), inspired by the monthly pictures of Nugget sent to the Duke population's emails by her caretaker Keith Upchurch. 
            Those emails would make any day or study session feel slightly better, and the only real regret I have as a Duke student is not having met her earlier. She cured my fear of dogs. And whenever
            I had something on my mind, seeing Nugget wag her tail near the West Union entrance would bring some joy to my day. And I imagine the entire Duke community has become a better place thanks to her.
            Amidst all the chaos that occurs on our campus, there is Nugget.</p>
            <p>This website is intended to bring a little bit of Nugget's radiant happiness into your life. Whether you can't meet Nugget amidst the COVID pandemic, you need a little bit of motivation,
            or want to make someone's day, I hope this website helps. Here's to you, Nugget. We love you.</p>
            <a href = "https://github.com/whydaniel/nuggetlovesyou">Repo behind this project (with dev details) is available here.</a>
            <br>
            <br>
            
