              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <p>Thank you for contributing content to Nugget Loves You. Please choose which content you'd like to submit. Please note that upon submission, your entry will need to be verified first before it can be displayed publicly. Have a good day!</p>
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="myTab" role="tablist">
              <li class="nav-item">
